-- Pacifix --

Pacifix receives the message, "Damn... Alright. Crossroads, Crotale, 
with me, NOW. Skullhammer, we wouldn't mind if you help us, see you 
there." Pacifix sprints through the corridors, and dashes out of the 
bases entrance. As soon as he passes throught the exit door, he 
transforms, "Pacifix, TRANSFORM!" and tears off at his top speed.

Crossroads is right behind, Pacifix, "Right away Pacifix, Crotale, 
get your can moving!" He whips out of the base, "Crossroads, 
transform!" and transforms into his Motorcycle mode, both tires 
burning rubber as dirt and rocks spray past the side of the 
base. "How far Pacifix?" he asks.

Pacifix checks, "According to the transmission, we're a fair 
distance from it, so we'll have to make good time."
